flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 46: Next.js Routing and Localization Architecture

  Req[Incoming request]
  Router[Next.js App Router]
  Detect[Resolve locale from URL, browser, and saved preference]
  Locale{Locale supported?}

  EN[Route group /en/...]
  BN[Route group /bn/...]
  Fallback[Redirect to default locale route]
  Persist[Persist locale preference after sign-in]

  RoleSeg[Role-scoped route segments]
  BuyerExp[Buyer experience pages]
  VendorExp[Vendor experience pages]
  AdminExp[Admin experience pages]

  Req --> Router --> Detect --> Locale
  Locale -- en --> EN --> Persist --> RoleSeg
  Locale -- bn --> BN --> Persist --> RoleSeg
  Locale -- no --> Fallback --> RoleSeg

  RoleSeg --> BuyerExp
  RoleSeg --> VendorExp
  RoleSeg --> AdminExp
